of%20re-appointment%2C%20rendering%20decision-making%20process%20bad%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20did%20not%20concern%20itself%20with%20the%20candidate's%20suitability.%20It%20only%20said%20that%20since%20the%20law%20conferred%20the%20Chancellor%20with%20the%20required%20competence%2C%20%26quot%3Bno%20other%20person%20can%20interfere%20with%20statutory%20authority%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kerala%20government%20and%20Governor%20have%20squabbled%20over%20the%20appointment%20of%20Vice%20Chancellors%20of%20state%20universities%20for%20over%20a%20year%2C%20dating%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkerala-news%2Fkerala-governor-seeks-resignation-of-9-universities-vice-chancellors-3457183%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMr%20Khan's%20October%202022%20order%20demanding%20nine%20resign%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20after%20the%20state%20appointed%20its%20own%20candidates%20as%20Vice%20Chancellors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaging-war-keralas-pinarayi-vijayan-slams-governors-latest-order-3458591%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BWaging%20War...%26quot%3B%3A%20Kerala's%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20Slams%20Governor's%20Latest%20Order%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ensuing%20spat%20saw%20the%20ruling%20Left%20Democratic%20Alliance%20and%20the%20opposition%20accuse%20each%20other%20of%20trying%20to%20insert%20their%20respective%20political%20ideologies%20into%20educational%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%20the%20Kerala%20Assembly%20passed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fkerala-university-bill%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUniversity%20Laws%20(Amendment)%20Bill%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20replaces%20the%20Governor%20as%20the%20Chancellor%20in%20favour%20of%20noted%20academicians.%20The%20state%20argued%20the%20Governor's%20move%20was%20an%20%26quot