said%20that%20it%20aims%20to%20learn%20from%20the%20experiences%20of%20the%20existing%20beneficiaries%20and%20also%20encompass%20those%20who%20have%20not%20yet%20availed%20the%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20the%20present%20government%20considers%20its%20citizens%20as%20'God'%20unlike%20the%20previous%20governments%20which%20saw%20themselves%20as%20parents%20to%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20people%20of%20the%20country%20have%20seen%20that%20period%20when%20the%20earlier%20governments%20considered%20themselves%20the%20parents%20of%20the%20people.%20Due%20to%20this%2C%20a%20large%20population%20of%20the%20country%20remained%20deprived%20of%20basic%20facilities%20for%20many%20decades%20after%20independence%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701334980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F14efqch4_modi_625x300_30_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fapni-kursi-sambhaliye-pm-modis-quip-during-interaction-with-jammu-sarpanch-4620848%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20interacted%20with%20beneficiaries%20of%20various%20government%20schemes%20and%20said%20how%20people%20have%20immense%20confidence%20in%20his%20government%20after%20the%20work%20they%20have%20done%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fapni-kursi-sambhaliye-pm-modis-quip-during-interaction-with-jammu-sarpanch-4620848%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fapni-kursi-sambhaliye-pm-modis-quip-during-interaction-with-jammu-sarpanch-4620848%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fapni-kursi-sambhaliye-pm-modis-quip-during-interaction-with-jammu-sarpanch-4620848%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russian%20missile%20st