%20of%20head%20coach%20Rahul%20Dravid%20and%20his%20staff%20on%20Wednesday.%20The%20contract%20of%20Dravid%20and%20his%20team%20had%20come%20to%20a%20conclusion%20with%20the%20end%20of%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023.%20While%20there%20were%20speculations%20over%20the%20BCCI's%20search%20for%20a%20new%20coach%2C%20all%20the%20parties%20settled%20on%20Dravid's%20extension%2C%20though%20the%20length%20of%20the%20contract%20isn't%20yet%20known.%20However%2C%20before%20Dravid%20put%20pen%20to%20paper%2C%20the%20BCCI%20did%20approach%20Gujarat%20Titans%20coach%20Ashish%20Nehra%20to%20take%20up%20head%20coach's%20role%20in%20the%20national%20team%20for%20the%20T20%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20confirmed%20to%20NDTV%20that%20Nehra%20was%20approached%20for%20the%20job%20but%20he%20rejected%20the%20offer%2C%20owing%20to%20his%20commitments%20with%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20franchise.%20A%20report%20in%20news%20agency%20PTI%20explained%20the%20reason%20behind%20Nehra's%20refusal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20must%20be%20mentioned%20that%20Gujarat%20Titans%20coach%20Ashish%20Nehra%20never%20had%20any%20intentions%20of%20being%20the%20head%20coach%20of%20the%20national%20team%20as%20he%20has%20always%20said%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bwants%20to%20honour%20his%20contract%20with%20GT%20till%202025%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehra%20has%20a%20young%20family%20and%20he%20doesn't%20want%20to%20live%20out%20of%20suitcase%20at%20the%20moment%20and%20being%20the%20India%20coach%20involves%20extensive%20travelling.%20Two%20and%20half%20months%20of%20IPL%20coaching%20is%20all%20he%20is%20looking%20at%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20future%20when%20the%20time%20is%20right%2C%20he%20might%20consider%20being%20a%20white-ball%20coach%20of%20national%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20interesting%20to%20see%20is%20that%20the%20length%20of%20Dravid's%20contract%20isn't%20yet%20known.%20It%20is%2C%20however%2C%20understood%20that%20Dravid%20would%20continue%20to%20guide%20the%20team%20till%20the%20conclusion%20of%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024.%20A%20decision%20over%20his%20association%20with%20the%20national%20team%20can%20be%20taken%20after%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehra's%20current%20contract%20with%20Gujarat%20Titans%2C%20his%20IPL%20franchise%2C%20runs%20till%202025.%20Considering%20the%20franchise%20has%20already%20lost%20its%20captain%20Hardik%20Pandya%20to%20Mumbai%20Indians%2C%20it%20is%20understandably%20tough%20for%20them%20to%20let%20go%20of%20their%20in-demand%20coach%20at%20this%20hour.%20Nehra%20had%20no%20intentions%20to%20force%20a%20move%20either%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701332640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fi7g7vnio_nehra_625x300_28_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwhy-ashish-nehra-rejected-bcci-s-t20-coach-offer-report-explains-4617330%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ashish%20Nehra%20was%20approached%20by%20the%20BCCI%20for%20the%20role%20of%20Coach%20in%20India's%20T20%20team.%20But%2C%20he%20rejected%20the%20proposal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwhy-ashish-nehra-rejected-bcci-s-t20-coach-offer-report-explains-4617330%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwhy-ashish-nehra-rejected-bcci-s-t20-coach-offer-report-explains-4617330%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwhy-ashish-nehra-rejected-bcci-s-t20-coach-offer-report-explains-4617330%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BPast%20Governments%20Considered%20Themselves%20Mai-Baap%20Of%20Citizens%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Modi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20said%20people%20have%20immense%20confidence%20in%20his%20government%20after%20looking%20at%20his%20work%20for%2010%20years%2C%20as%20he%20slammed%20the%20past%20dispensations%20for%20considering%20themselves%20%3Cem%3E'mai-baap'%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20citizens%20and%20working%20with%20vote%20bank%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20also%20said%20the%20four%20big%20'castes'%20for%20him%20are%20poor%2C%20youth%2C%20women%2C%20farmers%2C%20and%20asserted%20that%20their%20rise%20will%20make%20India%20developed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20the%20remarks%20after%20interacting%20with%20the%20'Viksit%20Bharat%20Sankalp%20Yatra'%20beneficiaries%20via%20video%20conferencing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EViksit%20Bharat%20Sankalp%20Yatra%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20being%20undertaken%20across%20the%20country%20with%20an%20aim%20to%20attain%20saturation%20of%20flagship%20schemes%20of%20the%20government%20by%20ensuring%20that%20the%20benefits%20of%20these%20schemes%20reach%20all%20targeted%20beneficiaries%20in%20a%20time%20bound%20manner%2C%20according%20to%20a%20statement%20issued%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20Office%20(PMO).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20remarks%20after%20interacting%20with%20the%20beneficiaries%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20Bharat%20is%20neither%20going%20to%20stop%20nor%20tire%20as%20the%20people%20of%20the%20country%20have%20resolved%20to%20make%20the%20country%20developed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20in%20various%20corners%20of%20the%20country%20there%20is%20such%20enthusiasm%20for%20the%20%3Cem%3Eyatra%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20there%20is%20for%20a%20reason%20for%20it%2C%20as%20people%20have%20seen%20(Narendra)%20Modi%2C%20his%20work%2C%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%20and%20therefore%2C%20they%20have%20immense%20confidence%20in%20the%20government%20and%20its%20efforts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20have%20also%20seen%20that%20period%20when%20earlier%20governments%20used%20to%20consider%20themselves%20%3Cem%3E'mai-baap'%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20people.%20Therefore%2C%20even%20after%20decades%20of%20independence%2C%20a%20big%20portion%20of%20the%20population%20was%20deprived%20of%20basic%20facilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMai-baap%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20Hindi%20term%20which%20loosely%20translates%20as%20a%20government%20having%20a%20feudal%20mindset.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20half%20the%20population%20had%20lost%20faith%20in%20governments%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20governments%20in%20the%20past%20used%20to%20look%20at%20political%20benefit%20and%20vote%20bank%20while%20undertaking%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTherefore%2C%20the%20people%20never%20used%20to%20trust%20the%20announcements%20of%20such%20%3Cem%3E'mai-baap'%3C%2Fem%3E%20governments.%20We%20have%20changed%20this%20and%20the%20government%20in%20place%20now%20considers%20people%20as%20form%20of%20God%20and%20we%20work%20with%20%3Cem%3E'seva%20bhav'%3C%2Fem%3E%20not%20%3Cem%3E'satta%20bhav'%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20in%20just%2015%20days%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3E'Viksit%20Bharat%20Sankalp%20Yatra'%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20people%20are%20walking%20along%20and%20joining%20it.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20are%20now%20identifying%20the%20%3Cem%3E'raths'%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Eyatra%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20the%20'Modi%20%3Cem%3Eki%20guarantee%20wali%20gaadi'%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20now%2C%20the%20vehicle%20of%20'Modi%20%3Cem%3Eki%20guarantee'%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reached%20over%2012%2C000%20panchayats%20and%20more%20than%2030%20lakh%20people%20have%20benefited%20from%20it%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMothers%20and%20sisters%20are%20reaching%20out%20to%20this%20vehicle%20of%20'Modi%20%3Cem%3Eki%20guarantee'%3C%2Fem%3E.%20People%20are%20giving%20this%20the%20shape%20of%20a%20people's%20movement%20and%20taking%20it%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20voice%20is%20heard%20across%20country%20that%20Modi's%20guarantee%20begins%20from%20where%20people's%20expectations%20from%20others%20end%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20event%2C%20PM%20Modi%20also%20launched%20an%20initiative%20to%20increase%20number%20of%20%3Cem%3EJan%20Aushadhi%20Kendras%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20sell%20medicines%20at%20subsidised%20rates%2C%20from%2010%2C000%20to%2025%2C000.%C2%A0%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20dedicated%20to%20the%20nation%20the%20landmark%2010%2C000th%20Jan%20Aushadi%20Kendra%20at%20AIIMS%2C%20Deoghar.%20He%20also%20launched%20the%20%3Cem%3E'Drone%20Didi%20Yojana'%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme%20aims%20to%20provide%20drones%20to%2015%2C000%20select%20women%20Self%20Help%20Groups%20during%20the%20period%202024-25%20to%202025-2026%20for%20providing%20rental%20services%20to%20farmers%20for%20agriculture%20purpose.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701332520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2Ffqtcu048_pm-modi-pti_625x300_28_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpast-governments-considered-themselves-mai-baap-of-citizens-pm-narendra-modi-4620538%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20said%20people%20have%20immense%20confidence%20in%20his%20government%20after%20looking%20at%20his%20work%20for%2010%20years%2C%20as%20he%20slammed%20the%20past%20dispensations%20for%20considering%20themselves%20'mai-baap'%20of%20citizens%20and%20working%20with%20vote%20bank%20in%20mind.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpast-governments-considered-themselves-mai-baap-of-citizens-pm-narendra-modi-4620538%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpast-gove