r%2C%20there%20is%20so%20much%20going%20on%20in%20the%20series%20that%20the%20murky%2C%20messy%20history%20of%20the%20marble%20mining%20town%20that%20the%20script%20seeks%20to%20dive%20into%20is%20often%20lost%20in%20a%20dense%20haze%20of%20opacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EShehar%20Lakhot%3C%2Fi%3E%20does%20not%20possess%20the%20depth%20and%20range%20of%20either%20Dahaad%20or%20Kohrra%2C%20but%20the%20show%20rustles%20up%20an%20array%20of%20characters%20that%20grab%20instant%20attention%20owing%20to%20the%20absorbing%20arcs%20that%20the%20script%20by%20Singh%20and%20Devika%20Bhagat%20is%20able%20to%20etch%20out%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20eight-part%20Amazon%20Prime%20Video%20show%20revolves%20around%20a%20man%20who%20calls%20himself%20a%20negotiator%20(he%20is%20not%20a%20fixer%2C%20he%20emphasises)%20and%20has%20a%20past%20that%20he%20is%20determined%20to%20live%20down.%20But%20circumstances%20conspire%20to%20bring%20him%20face%20to%20face%20with%20the%20realties%20that%20he%20wants%20to%20run%20away%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tetchy%20protagonist%2C%20Devendra%20Singh%20Tomar%20(played%20with%20restraint%20by%20Priyanshu%20Painyuli)%2C%20reluctantly%20makes%20his%20way%20back%20to%20his%20hometown%20in%20an%20SUV%20that%20his%20boss%20gifted%20to%20a%20demanding%20young%20mistress%20who%20wants%20her%20car%20back%20in%20one%20piece.%20He%20left%20Lakhot%20a%20decade%20ago%20and%20isn't%20sure%20it%20is%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20is%20the%20terrain%20that%20the%20vehicle%20that%20Dev%20drives%2C%20the%20family%20that%20he%20tries%20to%20reconnect%20with%20and%20the%20job%20that%20he%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20Lakhot%20for%20-%20ending%20a%20blockade%20of%20a%20marble%20mine%20by%20an%20agitated%20local%20tribe%20that%20has%20lived%20on%20the%20land%20for%20centuries%20-%20cause%20him%20and%20others%20no%20end%20of%20grief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20local%20activist%20Vikas%20Kachdaar%20(Chandan%20Roy)%20-%20he%20has%20a%20doctoral%20thesis%20on%20the%20social%20impact%20of%20mining%20under%20his%20belt%20-%20leads%20the%20protestors.%20He%20is%20the%20man%20that%20Dev%20negotiates%20with.%20But%20progress%20is%20painfully%20slow%20because%20Vikas%20refuses%20to%20abandon%20either%20the%20cause%20he%20espouses%20or%20the%20people%20he%20leads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakhot%20is%20poised%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20a%20development%20boom%20-%20a%20road%20is%20being%20built%20from%20the%20city%20to%20Kota%20and%20the%20inauguration%20of%20a%20new%20marble%20mine%20promises%20to%20open%20avenues%20of%20growth%20for%20its%20denizens%20-%20but%20its%20small-town%20ambience%20is%20hard%20to%20dispel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EShehar%20Lakhot%3C%2Fi%3E%20kicks%20off%20with%20the%20discovery%20of%20a%20White%20woman's%20body%20buried%20in%20a%20dry%2C%20dusty%2C%20desolate%20piece%20of%20land.%20Pallavi%20(Kubbra%20Sait)%20of%20the%20Lakhot%20police%20station's%20women%20cell%20ferrets%20around%20for%20clues%20even%20as%20the%20officer-in-charge%20Rajbir%20Rangot%20(Manu%20Rishi%20Chadha)%20wants%20her%20to%20close%20the%20case%20and%20move%20on.%20But%20she%2C%20the%20sole%20woman%20in%20a%20male-dominated%20police%20outpost%2C%20is%20persistent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20episode%20of%20%3Ci%3EShehar%20Lakhot%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20nearly%20an%20hour%20long%2C%20with%20the%20final%20one%20clocking%20a%20minute%20over%2070%20minutes.%20The%20series%20inevitably%20feels%20stretched%20and%20taxing%20at%20times.%20The%20writers%20are%20under%20constant%20pressure%20to%20keep%20the%20less%20effective%20passages%20from%20sticking%20out%20too%20prominently%20and%20undermining%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20series%20as%20a%20whole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fkd8D6mrekUk%3Fsi%3DZtVrSk7JErW8dd7c%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20parts%20and%20elements%20of%20the%20twisted%20tale%20that%20work%20-%20a%20few%20of%20the%20characters%20in%20particular%20and%20Dev's%20complex%20relationships%20with%20his%20father%20(Gyan%20Prakash)%2C%20elder%20brother%20Jayendra%20(Kashyap%20Shangari)%2C%20sister-in-law%20Vidushi%20(Shruti%20Jolly)%20and%20Sandhya%20(Shruthy%20Menon)%2C%20the%20girlfriend%20he%20left%20behind%20without%20so%20much%20as%20a%20by-your-leave%20-%20generate%20intrigue%20and%20suspense.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EShehar%20Lakhot%3C%2Fi%3E%20has%20three%20characters%20outside%20Dev's%20immediate%20orbit%20who%20add%20layers%20to%20the%20narrative%20-%20besides%20the%20smarmy%20cop%20Rajbir%20and%20the%20assiduous%20Pallavi%2C%20there%20is%20the%20unapologetically%20wicked%20Kairav%20Singh%20(Chandan%20Roy%20Sanyal).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKairav%20owns%20the%20marble%20mine%20that%20he%20claims%20will%20change%20Lakhot%20forever.%20He%20lives%20in%20a%20sprawling%20castle%20that%20doubles%20up%20as%20a%20heritage%20hotel%20where%20a%20slew%20of%20unseemly%20secrets%20lies%20buried.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mendacities%20and%20treacheries%2C%20the%20shenanigans%20of%20politicians%20and%20policemen%2C%20the%20deceit%20and%20deadly%20conspiracies%2C%20the%20conspiracies%20and%20betrayals%20flow%20thick%20and%20fast%20once%20the%20series%20gathers%20steam%20and%20plunges%20into%20an%20abyss%20of%20amorality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20male%20protagonist%20stands%20his%20ground%20despite%20being%20repeatedly%20roughed%20up.%20A%20tragedy%20compels%20him%20to%20dodge%20the%20law%20and%20vicious%20pursuers%2C%20among%20whom%20is%20a%20duo%20of%20siblings%2C%20Bhi%20(Manjiri%20Pupala)%20and%20Bho%20(Sanjay%20Shiv%20Narayan)%2C%20who%20work%20for%20Kairav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhi%2C%20who%20wields%20a%20bow%20and%20arrow%20with%20as%20proficiently%20as%20she%20handles%20firearms%2C%20is%20one%20of%20many%20women%20in%20Shehar%20Lakhot%20whose%20survival%20instincts%20border%20on%20the%20uncanny%2C%20resting%20as%20they%20do%20on%20the%20kind%20of%20meanness%20that%20stems%20of%20toxic%20masculinity.%20But%20not%20every%20woman%20in%20the%20series%20is%20her%20replica.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPallavi%20and%20Bhi%20represent%20two%20different%20worlds%20just%20as%20Sandhya%20and%20Vidushi%20do.%20Pallavi%20and%20Vidushi%20are%20good%20friends.%20The%20former%20is%20anything%20but%20feminine%20-%20a%20reflection%20of%20who%20she%20is%20in%20a%20man's%20world%3B%20the%20latter%20is%20a%20docile%2C%20soft-spoken%20homemaker%20who%20comes%20into%20her%20own%20when%20secrets%20begin%20to%20tumble%20out%20of%20her%20husband's%20closet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandhya's%20troubles%20are%20the%20most%20daunting.%20She%20is%20caught%20between%20two%20bickering%2C%20poles-apart%20brothers%20and%20between%20a%20man%20who%20wants%20to%20have%20Lakhot%20all%20to%20himself%20and%20another%20prodigal%20who%20wants%20to%20get%20away%20from%20it%20as%20soon%20as%20he%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlternating%20between%20the%20fascinating%20and%20the%20mechanical%2C%20Shehar%20Lakhot%20throws%20a%20few%20punches%20that%20land%20but%20it%20would%20have%20benefitted%20immensely%20from%20a%20shorter%20runtime.%20Is%20it%20good%20enough%20for%20a%20binge%3F%20It%20is%20because%20there%20is%20much%20in%20the%20series%20that%20goes%20beyond%20the%20limits%20of%20the%20genre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first-rate%20performances%20by%20an%20effectively%20edgy%20Priyanshu%20Painyuli%2C%20an%20understatedly%20beguiling%20Kubbra%20Sait%2C%20a%20consistent%20Manu%20Rishi%20Chadha%20and%20a%20superlatively%20classy%20Chandan%20Roy%20Sanyal%20(superb)%2C%20the%20fusion%20of%20crime%2C%20politics%2C%20police%20work%20and%20family%20dynamics%20in%20an%20environment%20in%20which%20nothing%20is%20what%20it%20seems%2C%20and%20the%20evocation%20of%20a%20lawless%20town%20in%20flux%20combine%20to%20make%20Shehar%20Lakhot%20watchable%20for%20the%20most%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%