0the%20initial%20public%20offer%20was%20fully%20subscribed%20in%20the%20first%2036%20minutes%20on%20the%20opening%20day%20on%20November%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IPO%20had%20a%20price%20band%20of%20Rs%20475-500%20per%20share.%20It%20was%20entirely%20an%20Offer%20For%20Sale%20(OFS)%20of%206.08%20crore%20equity%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETata%20Technologies%20is%20the%20first%20company%20from%20the%20Tata%20Group%20to%20launch%20an%20initial%20public%20offer%20in%20nearly%20two%20decades.%20Tata%20Consultancy%20Services%20was%20the%20last%20IPO%20from%20the%20Tata%20Group%20in%202004.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETata%20Technologies%20raised%20Rs%20791%20crore%20from%2067%20anchor%20investors.%20Fidelity%20International%2C%20BNP%20Paribas%2C%20Nippon%20Life%20India%2C%20HSBC%2C%20Kotak%2C%20SBI%20Mutual%20Fund%2C%20Motilal%20Oswal%2C%20Edelweiss%2C%20DSP%2C%20and%20Goldman%20Sachs%20were%20among%20others%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leading%20global%20provider%20of%20engineering%20solutions%2C%20boasts%20a%20robust%20track%20record%20of%20growth%20and%20profitability%2C%20coupled%20with%20a%20diversified%20clientele%20spanning%20various%20industries%2C%20including%20automotive%2C%20aerospace%2C%20and%20industrial%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETata%20Technologies%20offers%20product%20development%20and%20digital%20solutions%2C%20including%20turnkey%20solutions%2C%20to%20original%20equipment%20manufacturers.%20It%20is%20primarily%20focused%20on%20the%20automotive%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701331080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fltdjdpkg_tata-technologies_625x300_22_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftata-technologies-share-price-live-updates-stock-soars-180-in-debut-trade-4620403%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tata%20Technologies%20Ltd%20shares%20soared%20to%20an%20impressive%20180%20per%20cent%20above%20their%20issue%20price%20during%20their%20maiden%20trading%20sess