he%20company%20is%20in%20great%20hands%2C%20and%20I%20hope%20this%20is%20abundantly%20clear%20to%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cspan%3ELooking%20for%20a%20Plan%20B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20makes%20sense.%20The%20startup's%20near-death%20experience%20unsettled%20the%20companies%20and%20developers%20that%20have%20come%20to%20rely%20on%20OpenAI's%20artificial%20intelligence%20platform.%20Some%20of%20these%20partners%20started%20looking%20around%20for%20other%20providers.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3EA%20lot%20of%20friends%20of%20mine%20who%20were%20founders%20doing%20AI%2C%20basically%20look%20at%20this%20and%20go%2C%20we%20need%20a%20plan%20B%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20we%20can't%20depend%20on%20our%20entire%20stack%20on%20OpenAI%20models%2C%20because%20it%20could%20disappear%20tomorrow%2C%20just%20like%20it%20almost%20did%2C%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3B%20said%20Wesley%20Chan%2C%20cofounder%20of%20FPV%20Ventures.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20startup%20founders%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20they%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-startup-customers-considering-anthropic-meta-aimodels-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsidering%20switching%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-llama2-open-source-mark-zuckerberg-balls-replit-amjad-masad-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eopen%20source%20model%20like%20Meta's%20Llama%202%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-chatbot-google-chatgpt-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAnthropic's%20Claude%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20some%20said%20they%20were%20looking%20to%20switch%20cloud%20providers%20to%20Google%20or%20Amazon%20Web%20Services%20from%20Microsoft%20Azure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20'platform%20risk'%20of%20OpenAI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3EThis%20kind%20of%20drama%20just%20made%20some%20people%20think%20about%20their%20backup%20plan%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Guillermo%20Rauch%2C%20CEO%20of%20Vercel%2C%20a%20startup%20that%20helps%20developers%20build%20websites%20that%20integrate%20with%20many%20of%20the%20biggest%20AI%20models.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chaos%20made%20open-source%20AI%20models%20look%20more%20attractive%20because%20they%20rely%20on%20broad%20communities%20of%20contributors%2C%20rather%20than%20one%20startup%20that%20might%20suddenly%20lose%20all%20its%20employees.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWhat's%20the%20better%20wave%20to%20ride%20long%20term%3F%26quot%3B%20Rauch%20wrote%20in%20a%20message%20to%20BI.%20%26quot%3BOpen%20source%20(e.g.%3A%20Llama%20%2F%20Mistral)%2C%20whose%20reasoning%20power%20is%20less%20than%20OpenAI%2C%20but%20has%20the%20entire%20weight%20of%20a%20huge%20ecosystem%20behind%20it%2C%20or%20the%20proprietary%20LLMs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20height%20of%20the%20crisis%2C%20one%20of%20Vercel's%20AI%20engineering%20leads%20pinged%20Rauch%20to%20say%20%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3Elet's%20remove%20platform%20risk%20of%20OpenAI%26quot%3B%20and%20get%20a%20backup%20running%2C%20the%20CEO%20recalled.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20trend%20that%20has%20been%20cooking%2C%20and%20nothing%20was%20going%20to%20stop%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Rauch%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20feedback%20I'm%20getting%20from%20developers%20is%20that%20events%20like%20these%20make%20them%20re-prioritize%20and%20accelerate%20some%20of%20those%20explorations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cspan%3EExpunging%20doubts%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20OpenAI%20wants%20to%20become%20the%20next%20massive%20tech%20platform%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20expunge%20doubts%20like%20this%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible.%20And%20the%20best%20way%20to%20do%20that%20is%20to%20promise%20that%20the%20company%20will%20always%20be%20around%20%E2%80%94%20no%20matter%20who%20is%20CEO.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20enhance%20the%20governance%20structure%20of%20OpenAI%20so%20that%20all%20stakeholders%20%E2%80%93%20users%2C%20customers%2C%20employees%2C%20partners%2C%20and%20community%20members%20%E2%80%93%20can%20trust%20that%20OpenAI%20will%20continue%20to%20thrive%2C%26quot%3B%20Bret%20Taylor%2C%20the%20startup's%20new%20board%20chair%2C%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EMadeline%20Renbarger%20contributed%20to%20this%20article.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-less-powerful-openai-microsoft-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701327399000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65682e0c86933e8fdb2e3d0f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-less-powerful-openai-microsoft-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Silicon%20Valley%20just%20realized%20that%20the%20fate%20of%20OpenAI%20rested%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20only%20one%20person.%20It%20panicked%20and%20will%20no%20longer%20accept%20this%20situation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Alistair%20Barr)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-less-powerful-openai-microsoft-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Global%20Media%20Focuses%20on%20India-US%20Ties%20in%20Reports%20on%20US%20Indictment%20on%20Indian%20Officials'%20'Murder%20Plot'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30121410%2FUntitled-design-12-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20news%20of%20United%20States%E2%80%99%20federal%20pr