%20on%20its%20soil%2C%20U.S.%20relations%20with%20that%20government%20would%20plunge%20into%20crisis.%20But%20the%20relationship%20with%20India%20is%20a%20special%20case.%20%E2%80%A6%20It%E2%80%99s%20notable%20that%20once%20the%20administration%20found%20out%2C%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20scale%20down%20engagement%20with%20India.%20High-level%20meetings%20went%20on%20as%20scheduled%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Three%20such%20killings%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fus-unseals-indictment-sikh-killings-1.7043428%5C%22%3ECBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20noted%20that%20%E2%80%9C%5Bp%5Derhaps%20the%20most%20surprising%20allegation%20in%20the%20murder-for-hire%20indictment%20filed%20in%20New%20York%20state%20against%20Indian%20national%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20is%20a%20claim%20that%20there%20were%20plans%20to%20carry%20out%20three%20such%20killings%20on%20Canadian%20soil.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20details%20of%20the%20indictment%20that%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fpannun-assassination-plot-india-enquiry-committee-set-up%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%2C%20the%20CBC%20report%20says%20the%20plan%20to%20kill%20Pannu%20%E2%80%9Cchanged%20on%20June%2018%2C%E2%80%9D%20when%20masked%20gunmen%20murdered%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20outside%20a%20Sikh%20temple%20in%20British%20Columbia%2C%20according%20to%20the%20indictment%2C%20which%20adds%20that%20this%20made%20the%20killing%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpriority.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20mentions%20how%20the%20indictment%20has%20it%20that%20the%20Indian%20official%2C%20in%20a%20phone%20call%2C%20allegedly%20noted%20that%20a%20different%20hitman%20had%20handled%20it%20and%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20didn%E2%80%99t%20give%20to%20%5Bthe%20undercover%20officer%5D%20this%20job%2C%20so%20some%20other%20guy%20did%20this%20job%20%E2%80%A6