state%20under%20Republican%20President%20Richard%20Nixon.%20The%20German-born%20Jewish%20refugee's%20efforts%20led%20to%20the%20diplomatic%20opening%20of%20China%2C%20landmark%20U.S.-Soviet%20arms%20control%20talks%2C%20expanded%20ties%20between%20Israel%20and%20its%20Arab%20neighbours%2C%20and%20the%20Paris%20Peace%20Accords%20with%20North%20Vietnam%2C%20Reuters%20reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMr%20Kissinger%20was%20awarded%20the%20Nobel%20Peace%20Prize%20for%20negotiations%20to%20end%20the%20Vietnam%20War%2C%20even%20though%20the%20conflict%20did%20not%20immediately%20end%20and%20his%20North%20Vietnamese%20counterpart%2C%20Le%20Duc%20Tho%2C%20declined%20to%20accept%20the%20prize.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20the%20India-Pakistan%20War%20of%201971%2C%20Nixon%20and%20Kissinger%20were%20heavily%20criticised%20for%20tilting%20toward%20Pakistan.%20Kissinger%20was%20heard%20calling%20the%20Indians%20%26quot%3Bbastards%26quot%3B%20-%20a%20remark%20he%20later%20said%20he%20regretted.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701324660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Ftchg9ik_henry-kissinger_625x300_30_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhenry-kissinger-dies-at-100-5-facts-about-former-us-diplomat-4620219%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mr%20Kissinger%20played%20a%20pivotal%20and%20polarising%20role%20in%20US%20foreign%20policy%20during%20the%20Cold%20War.%20Mr%20Kissinger's%20family%20would%20hold%20a%20private%20funeral%2C%20with%20a%20memorial%20service%20to%20take%20place%20later%20in%20New%20York%2C%20where%20he%20grew%20up.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhenry-kissinger-dies-at-100-5-facts-about-former-us-diplomat-4620219%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhenry-kissinger-dies-at-100-5-facts-a