5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20306px)%2085vw%2C%20306px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22306%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22252%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20we%20inched%20closer%20to%20the%20election%20date%2C%20pollsters%20have%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20call%20the%20election%20in%20favour%20of%20any%20party.%20They%20expect%20a%20close%20fight%20between%20the%20BRS%20and%20Congress.%20Some%20surveys%20even%20do%20not%20rule%20out%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20hung%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20nervous%20BRS%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%2C%20which%20claims%20the%20sole%20credit%20for%20achieving%20statehood%20in%202014%2C%20has%20been%20in%20power%20for%20nearly%2010%20years.%20With%20K.%20Chandrashekhar%20Rao%20(KCR)%20at%20the%20helm%2C%20it%20has%20rolled%20out%20a%20slew%20of%20welfare%20measures%20and%20undertaken%20a%20number%20of%20development%20initiatives.%20According%20to%20BRS%2C%20it%20has%20been%20able%20to%20bring%20about%20a%20positive%20turnaround%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20people%20through%20equal%20thrust%20on%20welfare%20and%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20announcing%20its%20candidates%20almost%20three%20months%20back%20in%20August%2C%20the%20BRS%20was%20the%20first%20to%20hit%20the%20campaign%20trail%2C%20way%20ahead%20of%20others.%20Confident%20of%20winning%20a%20third%20term%2C%20the%20party%20has%20repeated%20almost%20all%20of%20its%20sitting%20MLAs%2C%20except%20for%20seven%20seats.%20The%20party%E2%80%99s%20narrative%20this%20election%20season%20has%20been%20around%20welfare%20schemes%20as%20well%20as%20%E2%80%98successes%E2%80%99%20the%20state%20has%20seen%20in%20the%20power%20and%20irrigation%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20flip%20side%2C%20the%20party%20has%20come%20under%20severe%20criticism%20from%20those%20who%20have%20been%20left%20out%20of%20welfare%20schemes.%20Welfare%20schemes%2C%20in%20a%20way%2C%20could%20prove%20counterproductive%20for%20the%20BRS%20given%20that%20there%20are%20a%20large%20number%20who%20are%20eligible%20yet%20have%20been%20left%20out.%20This%20has%20become%20particularly%20evident%20in%20schemes%20such%20as%20Dalit%20Bandhu%20and%20double-bedroom%20housing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20major%20criticism%20against%20BRS%20has%20been%20the%20perceived%20vice-grip%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20family%20holds%20on%20the%20levers%20of%20administration%20in%20the%20state%20and%20its%20alleged%20corruption.%20Many%20of%20the%20BRS%20MLAs%20are%20also%20accused%20of%20corruption%20in%20their%20constituencies.%20People%20on%20the%20ground%20allege%20that%20ruling%20party%20MLAs%20have%20been%20prioritising%20their%20cronies%20in%20welfare%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWidespread%20anger%20among%20unemployed%20youth%20in%20the%20state%20is%20palpable%2C%20and%20joblessness%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20key%20poll%20issue.%20Paper%20leaks%20during%20the%20conduct%20of%20recruitment%20exams%20and%20failure%20to%20fill%20vacancies%20in%20government%20departments%20have%20most%20youth%20disappointed%20with%20the%20KCR%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20perception%20of%20BRS%20being%20in%20a%20tacit%20understanding%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20on%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20and%20the%20AIMIM%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20could%20work%20against%20it%20among%20the%20Muslim%20and%20Christian%20minorities%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20resurgent%20Congress%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20which%20was%20down%20and%20out%20about%20six%20months%20ago%2C%20has%20made%20a%20surprising%20comeback.%20Since%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20victory%20in%20Karnataka%20in%20May%2C%20cadres%20and%20leaders%20in%20Telangana%20have%20received%20new%20vigour%20to%20go%20to%20the%20hustings.%20Besides%20a%20morale%20boost%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20victory%20has%20helped%20the%20party%20to%20strengthen%20its%20financial%20and%20organisational%20muscle%20to%20take%20on%20the%20BRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27132111%2FThe-Wire-91.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27132111%2FThe-Wire-91.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27132111%2FThe-Wire-91-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27132111%2FThe-Wire-91-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686533%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECongress%20leaders%20Mallu%20Bhatti%20Vikramarka%2C%20Revanth%20Reddy%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20among%20others.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40INCIndia%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20decline%20following%20the%20removal%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fare-cracks-appearing-in-bjps-telangana-unit-after-the-karnataka-debacle%5C%22%3EBandi%20Sanjay%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20Telangana%20unit%20chief%20in%20July%20this%20year%20is%20also%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%20for%20the%20Congress.%20The%20loss%20of%20momentum%20for%20the%20BJP%20has%20helped%20Congress%20to%20successfully%20drive%20home%20the%20point%20that%20only%20Congress%20can%20dethrone%20the%20BRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20messaging%20has%20been%20around%20two%20planks%3A%20one%2C%20on%20%3Cem%3Emaarpu%3C%2Fem%3E%20(change)%2C%20and%20two%2C%20by%20projecting%20itself%20as%20Telangana%20%3Cem%3Eichchina%3C%2Fem%3E%20party%20(the%20party%20that%20granted%20statehood).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%E2%80%99s%20manifesto%20also%20seems%20to%20have%20worked%20in%20developing%20a%20positive%20perception%20of%20itself.%20On%20the%20lines%20of%20its%20Karnataka%20manifesto%2C%20the%20party%20has%20announced%20six%20%E2%80%98guarantees%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20voters%20of%20Telangana.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20BRS%2C%20aware%20of%20the%20damage%20potential%20of%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20manifesto%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftelangana%2Fbrs-attempts-to-trump-congress-manifesto-with-few-more-novel-sops%2Farticle67424024.ece%5C%22%3Esought%20to%20outshine%20the%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0through%20its%20own%20manifesto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20is%20hopeful%20of%20support%20from%C2%A0youth%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Ftelanganas-exam-hub-trials-and-tribulations-of-job-aspirants-9033684%2F%5C%22%3Egovernment%20job%20aspirants%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20those%20left%20out%20of%20welfare%20schemes%3B%20and%20government%20employees%20who%20have%20been%20waiting%20for%20long%20for%20interim%20relief%2C%20restoration%20of%20the%20Old%20Pension%20Scheme%2C%20and%20Pay%20Revision%20Commission%20(PRC).%20Additionally%2C%20both%20Muslim%20and%20Christian%20minorities%20could%20also%20rally%20behind%20the%20Congress%20due%20to%20its%20effective%20messaging%20that%20the%20BRS%20and%20BJP%20are%20two%20sides%20of%20the%20same%20coin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20party%20faces%20a%20challenge%20on%20two%20fronts%3A%20BRS%E2%80%99s%20effective%20poll%20management%20and%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20possible%20role%20as%20a%20spoilsport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKingmaker%20BJP%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20fortunes%20over%20the%20last%20six%20months%20have%20diminished%20drastically.%20The%20momentum%20it%20had%20built%20with%20victories%20in%20multiple%20bypolls%20and%20its%20stellar%20performance%20in%20the%20election%20to%20the%20Greater%20Hyderabad%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(GHMC)%20had%20given%20rise%20to%20a%20perception%20that%20it%20was%20the%20principal%20challenger%20to%20the%20incumbent%20BRS.%20However%2C%20the%20easing%20out%20of%20Sanjay%20as%20the%20state%20party%20chief%2C%20factionalism%20in%20the%20state%20leadership%2C%20and%20the%20perception%20that%20the%20central%20leadership%20is%20soft%20on%20the%20BRS%20have%20resulted%20in%20its%20momentum%20being%20fizzled%20out.%20Various%20surveys%20indicate%20that%20it%20could%20emerge%20as%20a%20distant%20third.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20party%20is%20hopeful%20of%20giving%20a%20tough%20fight%20in%20several%20constituencies%2C%20thereby%20affecting%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20prospects.%20In%20particular%2C%20it%20is%20expected%20to%20face%20a%20stiff%20fight%20for%20anti-BRS%20votes%20in%20about%2020%20seats%2C%20including%20in%20Korutla%2C%20LB%20Nagar%2C%20Bodhan%2C%20Kamareddy%2C%20Nirmal%2C%20Maheshwaram%2C%20and%20in%20a%20few%20handful%20of%20seats%20of%20the%20Greater%20Hyderabad%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(GHMC).%20With%20a%20hung%20assembly%20not%20ruled%20out%2C%20the%20BJP%20believes%20that%20it%20would%20be%20in%20a%20position%20to%20emerge%20as%20the%20kingmaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701307848000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29221132%2FEffect-4.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-voting-day-close-fight-brs-congress%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20BRS%20and%20Congress%20are%20the%20main%20contenders%2C%20the%20BJP%20could%20well%20emerge%20as%20the%20kingmaker%20by%20eating%20into%20the%20anti-BRS%20vote.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-voting-day-close-fight-brs-congress%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Narayana%20Murthy%E2%80%99s%2070-Hour%20Work%20Week%20Proposal%20Is%20Emblematic%20of%20a%20Deeper%20Issue%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29161037%2Fnrn.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EInfosys%20co-founder%20N.R.%20Narayana%20Murthy%20recently%20sparked%20a%20debate%20by%20suggesting%20that%20Indian%20youngsters%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2F2023%2F10%2F30%2Finfosys-founder-narayana-murthy-young-indians-70-hour-work-week%2F%5C%22%3Eshould%20work%2070%20hours%20a%20week%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20the%20nation%20could%20compete%20with%20other%20developed%20nations.%20A%20senior%20congress%20MP%2C%20Manish%20Tewari%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Flatest%2Fcorporate%2Fstory%2Fwhats-wrong-with-it-congress-manish-tewari-says-70-hr-work-week-15-vacations-a-year-must-become-norm-405371-2023-11-10%5C%22%3Ebacked%20the%20idea%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20arguing%20working%20long%20hours%20should%20in%20fact%20become%20the%20norm.%20Many%20industrial%20stalwarts%20along%20with%20Bollywood%20actors%20have%20also%20lent%20their%20support%20to%20Murthy%E2%80%99s%20proposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomehow%2C%20working%20long%20hours%20is%20equated%20with%20%E2%80%98development%E2%80%99.%20While%20many%20experts%20have%20already%20discussed%20the%20merits%20and%20demerits%20of%20this%20proposition%2C%20a%20key%20element%20that%20has%20been%20missing%20in%20the%20discourse%20is%20our%20(mis)conception%20of%20work%2C%20labour%20and%20value.%20Fears%20associated%20to%20working%20less%20share%20similarities%20with%20the%20ongoing%20debate%20surrounding%20unconditional%20welfare%20proposals%20like%20a%20basic%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDecoding%20the%20meaning%20of%20value%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20key%20criticisms%20of%20unconditional%20welfare%20is%20that%20it%20can%20discourage%20people%20from%20making%20a%20%E2%80%98valuable%20contribution%E2%80%99%20to%20society.%20Only%20when%20everyone%20contributes%20to%20the%20economy%20can%20the%20system%20of%20cooperative%20production%20be%20sustained%20and%20lead%20to%20more%20progress%2C%20it%20is%20argued.%20For%20people%20like%20Murthy%2C%20this%20is%20precisely%20why%20working%20longer%20hours%20makes%20sense%2C%20for%20it%20allows%20us%20to%20pump%20in%20more%20%E2%80%98value%E2%80%99%20into%20the%20economy%20and%20generate%20better%20income%20outcomes.%20We%20see%20echoes%20of%20this%20line%20of%20thinking%20in%20Hayek%E2%80%99s%20understanding%20of%20value%2C%20the%2020th%20century%20libertarian%20economist%20who%20is%20renowned%20for%20his%20criticism%20of%20Keynesian%20economics.%20He%20argues%20that%20value%20is%20simply%20determined%20by%20demand%20and%20supply%20forces%20of%20the%20market%20i.e.%2C%20a%20measure%20of%20%E2%80%9Cwhat%20consumers%20are%20willing%20to%20pay%20for%20this%20or%20that%20good%E2%80%9D.%20Hence%2C%20incomes%20or%20wages%20are%20proportional%20to%20one%E2%80%99s%20contribution%2C%20determined%20by%20demand%20and%20supply%20contingencies.%20Murthy%E2%80%99s%20proposition%2C%20in%20essence%2C%20is%20inspired%20by%20the%20philosophy%20that%20engaging%20in%20labour%20is%20deemed%20a%20prerequisite%20for%20generating%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22'Minimum%20Income'%20in%20India%20Must%20Come%20Through%20Jobs%2C%20Public%20Services%20and%20Pensions%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Fminimum-income-in-india-must-come-through-jobs-public-services-and-pensions%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Minimum%20Income%E2%80%99%20in%20India%20Must%20Come%20Through%20Jobs%2C%20Public%20Services%20and%20Pensions%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20market-based%20conception%20of%20value%20stands%20on%20a%20hollow%20premise.%20Nothing%20tells%20us%20why%20satiating%20the%20market%20demand%20is%20equivalent%20to%20making%20a%20valuable%20contribution%2C%20something%20that%20Hayek%20and%20Murthy%20take%20for%20granted.%20While%20many%20economists%20justify%20this%20in%20the%20garb%20of%20%E2%80%98economic%20growth%E2%80%99%2C%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20why%20the%20market%20is%20considered%20as%20the%20source%20of%20all%20value.%20Performing%20labour%2C%20in%20whichever%20form%20it%20may%20be%2C%20is%20deemed%20as%20essential%2C%20without%20which%20we%20cannot%20think%20of%20doing%20anything%20meaningful%20or%20valuable%20with%20our%20lives%20in%20this%20current%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProblematising%20%E2%80%98market%20value%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20problems%20emerge%20from%20this%20narrow%20conceptualisation%20of%20value.%20First%2C%20it%20lends%20credence%20to%20income%20inequality%2C%20since%20income%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20reflection%20of%20demand%20in%20the%20market.%20Certain%20occupations%20are%2C%20hence%2C%20considered%20more%20valuable%20in%20nature.%20A%20venture%20capitalist%20earning%20a%20significantly%20higher%20income%20over%20that%20of%20a%20teacher%20(who%20is%20likely%20to%20drive%20a%20greater%20social%20impact)%20is%20very%20well%20justified%20under%20this%20framework%20since%20considerations%20of%20justice%20and%20moral%20desert%20do%20not%20apply%20to%20the%20market.%20This%20makes%20Hayek%20argue%20that%20inequalities%20are%20an%20acceptable%20product%20of%20this%20arrangement%20which%20should%20not%20be%20corrected%20through%20redistributive%20measures%20because%20they%20have%20a%20legitimate%20grounding%20in%20economic%20value%20decided%20by%20the%20market%20forces.%20But%20on%20what%20grounds%20is%20an%20asset%20manager%20rewarded%20more%20by%20the%20market%20as%20compared%20to%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20an%20ASHA%20worker%2C%20is%20simply%20not%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20following%20from%20this%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20markets%20can%20many%20times%20be%20brutal%20in%20assigning%20a%20value%20to%20one%E2%80%99s%20contribution%20and%20very%20unreasonably%20justify%20inequalities.%20Against%20this%20backdrop%2C%20Murthy%E2%80%99s%20proposition%20for%20Indians%20to%20work%20long%20hours%20reeks%20of%20ignorance%20and%20entitlement.%20On%20an%20average%2C%20gig%20workers%20in%20India%20dedicate%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fgig-workers-long-hours-little-pay-scant-security%2Fcid%2F1905851%5C%22%3E12%20hours%20to%20their%20work%20every%20day%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20already%20way%20above%20the%20recommended%20eight-hour%20daily%20limit%20stipulated%20by%20labour%20laws%20and%20exceeds%20Murthy%E2%80%99s%20suggested%2070-hour%20workweek.%20Worse%2C%20the%20current%20economic%20setup%20with%20market%E2%80%99s%20dictatorial%20tendencies%20fails%20to%20reward%20the%20workers%20adequately%2C%20with%20many%20workers%20complaining%20about%20burnouts%20and%20earning%20a%20measly%20pay%20despite%20the%20time%20and%20effort%20they%20put%20in%20daily.%20Such%20examples%20demonstrate%20that%20extending%20working%20hours%20may%20not%20be%20a%20solution%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20developmental%20problems%2C%20and%20could%20potentially%20exacerbate%20the%20situation%20instead.%20Notably%2C%20with%2085%25%20of%20the%20workforce%20being%20in%20the%20informal%20economy%2C%20most%20Indians%20are%20already%20working%20long%20hours%20for%20which%20they%20are%20not%20adequately%20remunerated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERedefining%20value%20and%20a%20case%20for%20UBI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20confining%20ourselves%20to%20the%20market%20forces%2C%20we%20narrow%20our%20possibilities%20for%20measuring%20value.%20We%20need%20to%20reconceptualise%20our%20current%20understanding%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20worth%2C%20one%20that%20allows%20individuals%20to%20make%20life%20decisions%20free%20from%20the%20constraints%20of%20market%20dynamics%20and%20to%20embrace%20diverse%20forms%20of%20work%2C%20activities%2C%20and%20lifestyles.%20Murthy%E2%80%99s%20suggestion%20for%20extended%20working%20hours%20is%20emblematic%20of%20a%20deeper%20problem%20of%20a%20narrow%20interpretation%20of%20the%20value%20of%20work%2C%20one%20that%20predefines%20the%20purpose%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20labour.%20This%20perspective%20overlooks%20the%20various%20paths%20to%20leading%20a%20fulfilling%20life%20which%20fails%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20diversity%20in%20what%20constitutes%20a%20meaningful%20existence.%20As%20Marx%20rightly%20puts%20it%2C%20%E2%80%9Cemancipation%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20not%20only%20being%20free%20from%20work%20but%20also%20of%20being%20free%20to%20work%20in%20light%20of%20the%20ends%20that%20matter%20to%20us%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20promoting%20the%20idea%20of%20extending%20working%20hours%2C%20we%20should%20explore%20proposals%20that%20empower%20individuals%20to%20freely%20define%20the%20contours%20of%20their%20work%20time%20and%20labor%20power%2C%20so%20they%20can%20pursue%20goals%20which%20are%20aligned%20with%20their%20personal%20visions%20of%20a%20fulfilling%20and%20meaningful%20life.%20Proposals%20like%20%E2%80%98Universal%20Basic%20Income%E2%80%99%20(UBI)%20offer%20a%20solution%20by%20providing%20a%20social%20security%20floor%2C%20ensuring%20individuals%20are%20not%20coerced%20into%20meaningless%20jobs.%20UBI%20allows%20for%20the%20prioritisation%20of%20personal%20freedom%20and%20the%20pursuit%20of%20activities%20with%20intrinsic%20value%2C%20shifting%20our%20barometer%20of%20value%20from%20market-oriented%20to%20one%20centred%20on%20the%20freedom%20to%20define%20a%20fulfilling%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAkshat%20Sogani%20is%20a%20former%20LAMP%20fellow%20and%20Ashoka%20alumni%2C%20currently%20working%20as%20a%20policy%20consultant.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701307806000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29161037%2Fnrn.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fwhy-narayana-murthys-70-hour-work-week-proposal-is-emblematic-of-a-deeper-issue%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22By%20confining%20ourselves%20to%20the%20market%20forces%2C%20we%20narrow%20our%20possibilities%20for%20measuring%20value.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fwhy-narayana-murthys-70-hour-work-week-proposal-is-emblematic-of-a-deeper-issue%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20economy%20expected%20to%20sustain%20strong%20growth%20amid%20global%20gloom%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701306807000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-08%2F19%2Ffull%2F1660933146-9194.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findian-economy-expected-to-sustain-strong-growth-amid-global-gloom-123113000058_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20is%20seen%20as%20the%20bright%20spot%20globally%20as%20some%20Western%20countries%20are%20flirting%20with%20the%20possibility%20of%20recession%2C%20while%20China%2C%20the%20world's%20second-largest%20economy%2C%20has%20slowed%20down%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findian-economy-expected-to-sustain-strong-growth-amid-global-gloom-123113000058_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%