uding%20high-profile%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20held%20by%20Israel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Ftalks-on-in-qatar-to-extend-truce%2Farticleshow%2F105602713.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Ftalks-on-in-qatar-to-extend-truce%2Famp_articleshow%2F105602713.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Ftalks-on-in-qatar-to-extend-truce%2Famp_articleshow%2F105602713.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Justice%20Department%E2%80%99s%20Timeline%3A%20How%20Indian%20Official%20'Plotted'%20to%20Kill%20Khalistan%20Activists%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30010249%2Findictment.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20November%2029%2C%20federal%20prosecutors%20in%20the%20US%20filed%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fpannun-assassination-plot-india-enquiry-committee-set-up%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eexplosive%20charges%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20a%20New%20York%20court%20which%20detailed%20how%20a%20plot%20to%20kill%20a%20US%20citizen%20who%20runs%20a%20pro-Khalistan%20organisation%2C%20ordered%20by%20an%20%E2%80%9Cidentified%20Indian%20government%20employee%E2%80%9D%2C%20was%20thwarted%20by%20US%20law%20enforcement%20agencies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20target%2C%20identified%20in%20the%20indictment%20only%20as%20%E2%80%98the%20Victim%E2%80%99%2C%20is%20apparently%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20the%20general%20counsel%20for%20Sikhs%20for%20Justice%2C%20a%20group%20that%20is%20banned%20in%20India.%20The%20plotters%20identified%20by%20the%20US%20prosecutors%20are%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20an%20Indian%20national%2C%20and%20%E2%80%98CC-1%E2%80%99%2C%20an%20Indian%20government%20employee.%20Both%20were%20based%20in%20India%20and%20directed%20the%20operation%20from%20here.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGupta%20is%20described%20as%20an%20associate%20of%20CC-1%20who%20claims%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20international%20narcotics%20and%20weapons%20trafficking.%20The%20Indian%20official%20is%20described%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Cidentified%20Indian%20government%20agency%20employee%20who%20has%20variously%20described%20himself%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98Senior%20Field%20Officer%E2%80%99%20with%20responsibilities%20in%20%E2%80%98Security%20Management%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Intelligence%2C%E2%80%99%20and%20who%20also%20has%20referenced%20previously%20serving%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20and%20receiving%20%E2%80%9Cofficer%5B%5D%20training%E2%80%9D%20in%20%E2%80%9Cbattle%20craft%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cweapons%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGupta%20contacted%20an%20individual%20(%E2%80%9CCS%E2%80%9D)%20who%20he%20believed%20was%20a%20criminal%20associate%2C%20but%20who%20was%20in%20fact%20a%20confidential%20source%20working%20with%20US%20law%20enforcement.%20Gupta%20contacted%20CS%20for%20assistance%20in%20contracting%20a%20hitman%20to%20murder%20the%20Victim%20in%20New%20York%20City.%20The%20CS%20introduced%20Gupta%20to%20a%20purported%20hitman%2C%20who%20was%20in%20fact%20an%20undercover%20US%20law%20enforcement%20officer%20(the%20%E2%80%9CUC%E2%80%9D).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20following%20is%20a%20timeline%20of%20events%2C%20as%20alleged%20by%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice.%20It%20begins%20with%20CC-1%20recruiting%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20in%20early%20May%20this%20year%2C%20to%20the%20filing%20charges%20related%20to%20the%20thwarted%20plot%20on%20November%2029.%20The%20Indian%20government%20official%20and%20Gupta%20also%20drop%20hints%2C%20as%20per%20the%20charges%2C%20that%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20who%20was%20killed%20in%20a%20shooting%20outside%20a%20gurdwara%20in%20British%20Columbia%20in%20June%2C%20was%20their%20%E2%80%98target%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20well%20plans%20to%20hit%20other%20%E2%80%98targets%E2%80%99%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EEarly%20May%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20a%20series%20of%20telephonic%20and%20electronic%20communications%20between%20CC-1%20and%20Gupta%20over%20encrypted%20applications%2C%20CC-1%20asks%20Gupta%20to%20arrange%20the%20murder%20of%20the%20Victim%20in%20exchange%20for%20CC-1%E2%80%99s%20assistance%20in%20securing%20the%20dismissal%20of%20a%20criminal%20case%20against%20Gupta%20in%20India.%20Gupta%20agrees%20to%20orchestrate%20the%20assassination.%20Gupta%20also%20met%20CC-1%20in%20person%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMay%206%2C%202023%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3ECC-1%20messages%20Gupta%20over%20an%20encrypted%20messaging%20application%20about%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctarget%20in%20New%20York%E2%80%9D%20and%20another%20target%20in%20%E2%80%9CCalifornia.%E2%80%9D%20Gupta%20replies%3A%20%E2%80%9DWe%20will%20hit%20our%20all%20Targets.%E2%80%9D%20The%20telephone%20number%20used%20by%20CC-1%20has%20an%20India%20country%20code%20and%20is%20registered%20to%20an%20email%20account%20that%20accessed%20the%20Internet%20during%20the%20period%20of%20the%20murder%20plot%20on%20numerous%20occasions%20from%20the%20vicinity%20of%20New%20Delhi.%20CC-1%20worked%20during%20the%20relevant%20time%20period%20for%20an%20Indian%20government%20agency.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMay%2012%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20CC-1%20tells%20Gupta%20that%20his%20criminal%20case%20%E2%80%9Chas%20already%20been%20taken%20care%20of%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9Cnobody%20from%20Gujrat%20(sic)%20police%20is%20calling.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMay%2023%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20CC-1%20again%20assures%20Gupta%20that%20he%20had%20%E2%80%9Cspoke%5Bn%5D%20with%20the%20boss%E2%80%9D%20about%20the%20Gujarat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ecase%20and%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Call%20clear%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cnobody%20will%20ever%20bother%20you%20again.%E2%80%9D%20CC-1%20offers%20to%20arrange%20a%20meeting%20between%20Gupta%20and%20a%20deputy%20commissioner%20of%20police.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMay%2029%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Gupta%20asks%20the%20CS%20by%20phone%20if%20the%20CS%20knew%20anyone%20who%20would%20be%20willing%20to%20carry%20out%20a%20murder-for-hire%20in%20the%20US.%20Gupta%20explains%20that%20the%20intended%20victim%20was%20a%20lawyer%20who%20split%20time%20between%20New%20York%20City%20and%20another%20US%20city.%20The%20CS%20says%20he%20will%20reach%20out%20to%20his%20contacts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMay%2029%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Gupta%20messages%20the%20CS%20the%20Victim%E2%80%99s%20name%20and%20other%20information%20about%20the%20Victim.%20Says%20the%20Victim%20spent%20most%20of%20his%20time%20in%20New%20York.%20In%20response%2C%20the%20CS%20asks%20Gupta%20for%20additional%20information%20about%20the%20Victim%20and%20details%20about%20payment%20for%20the%20murder.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMay%2029%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Gupta%20sends%20screenshots%20to%20CC-1%20of%20his%20text%20messages%20with%20the%20CS%20requesting%20details%20about%20the%20Victim%20and%20about%20payment%20for%20killing%20the%20Victim.%20CC-1%20says%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20are%20ready%20to%20pay%20%24150000%E2%80%A6%20the%20offer%20will%20go%20higher%20depending%20upon%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20work%E2%80%A6and%20if%20it%E2%80%99s%20done%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%E2%80%9D%20GUPTA%20replies%20to%20CC-1%20with%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20CS%20requesting%20%E2%80%9C100%20k.%E2%80%9D%20CC-I%20responded%20%E2%80%9COk%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20then%20added%20that%20while%20an%20advance%20payment%20was%20not%20possible%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20whole%20money%20will%20be%20paid%20with%20in%20%5Bsic%5D%2024%20hours%20after%20the%20work%20is%20done.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EJune%201%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20CC-1%20sends%20Gupta%20the%20street%20address%20for%20the%20Victim%E2%80%99s%20home%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20which%20CC-1%20describes%20to%20Gupta%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20locality%20of%20%5Bthe%20Victim%E2%80%99s%5D%20House.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EJune%202%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20CC-1%20messages%20Gupta%2C%20asking%20for%20%E2%80%9Cany%20update%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20murder%20plot%2C%20stating%20%E2%80%9C%5Bi%5Dt%E2%80%99s%20important%20and%20less%20time.%E2%80%9D%20Gupta%20responds%20that%20he%20expected%20to%20have%20an%20update%20the%20following%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EJune%203%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Gupta%20urges%20CS%20over%20an%20audio%20call%20to%20have%20his%20associates%20carry%20out%20the%20murder%20soon%2C%20stating%3A%20%E2%80%9Cfinish%20him%20brother%2C%20finish%20him%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20take%20too%20much%20time%20%E2%80%A6%20push%20these%20guys%2C%20push%20these%20guys%20%E2%80%A6%2C%20finish%20the%20job.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EJune%203%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Gupta%20informs%20CC-1%20that%20he%20has%20%E2%80%9Cspoke%5Bn%5D%20with%20the%20NY%20group%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Ctold%20them%20they%20have%20to%20discharge%20%5Bthe%20Victim%5D%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EJune%204%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Gupta%20speaks%20with%20the%20CS%20by%20audio%20call%2C%20and%20promises%20the%20CS%20that%20%E2%80%9Cif%20this%20job%20is%20done%20successfully%E2%80%9D%20then%20he%20will%20%E2%80%9Cbring%20the%20chief%E2%80%99%20to%20meet%20the%20CS.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJune%204%2C%202023%3A%20CS%20sends%20Gupta%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpurported%20surveillance%20photograph%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Victim%20as%20proof%20that%20the%20CS%E2%80%99s%20New%20York%20associates%20were%20monitoring%20the%20Victim%20and%20that%20the%20Victim%20would%20be%20killed%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20received%20an%20advance%20payment%20of%20%2425%2C000.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EJune%205%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Gupta%20sends%20the%20surveillance%20photo%20and%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20CS%E2%80%99s%20messages%20to%20CC-1.%20Gupta%20asks%20CC-1%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccheck%20with%20%5Bhis%5D%20NY%20dealer%20if%20he%20can%20arrange%20the%2025k%20%5Bpayment%5D%20there.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EJune%206%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Gupta%20messages%20the%20CS%20asking%20to%20be%20put%20directly%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20CS%E2%80%99s%20New%20York%20associates%2C%20who%20will%20receive%20the%20advance%20payment%20and%20carry%20out%20the%20murder.%20The%20CS%20introduces%20Gupta%20through%20electronic%20messages%20to%20the%20UC%2C%20who%20was%20purporting%20to%20be%20the%20CS%E2%80%99s%20associate%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EJune%206%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20On%20an%20audio%20call%2C%20Gupta%20instructs%20the%20CS%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20need%20to%20calm%20down%20everything%2010%20days%E2%80%9D%20because%20of%20engagements%20between%20high-level%20government%20officials%20of%20Indian%20and%20the%20US%20scheduled%20to%20occur%20over%20the%20ensuing%20weeks.%20Gupta%20explains%20that%20given%20the%20Victim%E2%80%99s%20public%20profile%20as%20an%20activist%2C%20there%20could%20be%20protests%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20his%20death%20and%20could%20lead%20to%20geopolitical%20fallout%20if%20the%20Victim%20were%20assassinated%20on%20US%20soil%20during%20those%20planned%20meetings.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EJune%208%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20CC-1%20sends%20Gupta%20the%20name%20of%20an%20associate%20(Individual-1)%20and%20the%20associate%E2%80%99s%20phone%20number%20with%20an%20Indian%20c