%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20looks%20promising..%20but%20we%20have%20today%20only..%20if%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20happen%20today%20it%20will%20be%20done%20after%20%5BJune%5D%2024%2C%E2%80%9D%20i.e.%2C%20after%20the%20engagements%20between%20the%20Indian%20and%20US%20governments%20are%20completed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EJune%2012%3A%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Gupta%20indicates%20that%20his%20co-conspirators%20who%20are%20directing%20the%20assassination%20plot%20from%20India%20have%20extensive%20resources%20and%20were%20closely%20monitoring%20the%20progress.%20UC%20receives%20a%20video%20call%20from%20Gupta%2C%20who%20appeared%20to%20be%20in%20a%20conference%20room.%20Gupta%20shows%20%E2%80%9Cthree%20other%20men%20in%20the%20room%20who%20were%20dressed%20in%20business%20attire%2C%20sitting%20around%20a%20conference%20table%E2%80%9D.%20Gupta%20tells%20the%20UC%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20are%20all%20counting%20on%20you.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EJune%2012%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20On%20a%20call%20with%20the%20CS%2C%20Gupta%20states%20that%20there%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbig%20target%E2%80%9D%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EJune%2014%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Gupta%20messages%20the%20CS%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20will%20be%20needing%20one%20good%20team%20in%20Canada%20also%2C%20%5Bt%5Domorrow%20I%20will%20share%20you%20the%20details.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EJune%2015%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Gupta%20advises%20the%20CS%20by%20phone%20that%20he%20was%20still%20%E2%80%9Cwaiting%20%5Bfor%5D%20the%20details%E2%80%9D%20about%20the%20Canadian%20target.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EJune%2016%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Gupta%20tells%20the%20CS%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20are%20doing%20their%20job%2C%20brother.%20We%20are%20doing%20their%20New%20York%20%5Band%5D%20Canada%20%5Bjob%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20referring%20to%20the%20individuals%20directing%20the%20plots%20from%20India.%3C%2Fspan