wholly%20misconceived%20PIL.%20We%20fail%20to%20understand%20as%20to%20how%20the%20human%20voice%20making%20azaan%20through%20loudspeakers%20could%20achieve%20the%20decibels%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20creating%20noise%20pollution%20causing%20health%20hazard%20for%20%5Bthe%5D%20public%20at%20large%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chief%20Justice%20Agarwal%20said%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDharmendra%20Prajapati%2C%20the%20man%20who%20filed%20the%20PIL%2C%20said%20that%20he%20objected%20to%20azaan%20playing%20five%20times%20a%20day%20near%20the%20hospital%20he%20worked%20in%20and%20that%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fahmedabad%2Fazaan-on-loudspeakers-no-noise-pollution-high-court%2Farticleshow%2F105572982.cms%5C%22%3Ecaused%20disturbance%20to%20patients%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fhigh-court%2Fgujarat-high-court%2Fmosque-loudspeaker-ban-gujarat-high-court-pil-dismissed-azaanmuslimfaith-243217%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20legal%20news%20website%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20Agarwal%20asked%20the%20petitioner%E2%80%99s%20counsel%20what%20they%20believed%20azaan%E2%80%99s%20decibel%20levels%20tend%20to%20be%2C%20following%20which%20the%20counsel%20said%20it%20exceeded%20the%20%E2%80%98decibel%20limit%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYour%20DJ%20creates%20a%20lot%20of%20pollution.%20We%20are%20not%20entertaining%20this%20kind%20of%20PIL.%20It%20is%20a%20faith%20and%20practice%20going%20on%20%5Bfor%5D%20years%20together%20and%20it%20is%20a%20moment%20of%20only%20five%20to%2010%20minutes.%20Azaan%20goes%20on%20for%20less%20than%2010%20minutes%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20chief%20justice%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Prajapati%E2%80%99s%20counsel%20argued%20that%20azaan%20happened%20multiple%20times%20a%20day%20unlike%20%3Cem%3Eaarti%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20temples%2C%20the%20chief%20justice%20asked%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%20if%20aarti%20did%20not%20likewise%20create%20disturbance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20in%20your%20temples%2C%20the%20morning%20aarti%20with%20those%20drums%20and%20music%20that%20starts%20early%20morning.%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20cause%20any%20noise%20or%20disturbance%20to%20anyone%3F%20Can%20you%20say%20that%20the%20noise%20of%20that%20%3Cem%3Eghanta%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5Bbells%5D%20and%20%3Cem%3Eghadiyal%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5Bgong%5D%20stays%20within%20temple%20premises%20and%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20percolate%20out%20of%20the%20premises%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20noise%20pollution%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cscientific%20issue%E2%80%9D%20and%20asked%20the%20petitioner%20if%20scientific%20methods%20of%20measuring%20noise%20pollution%20could%20corroborate%20his%20argument.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20can%20argue%20this%2C%20we%20will%20permit%20you.%20But%20you%20are%20not%20arguing%20this.%20You%20have%20not%20made%20out%20any%20base%20in%20the%20writ%20petition.%20Where%20is%20the%20pleading%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20decibels%3F%20Where%20is%20the%20pleading%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20scientific%20method%20of%20assessment%20of%20noise%20pollution%20in%20the%20area%3F%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20order%20on%20the%20matter%20said%20according%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20concluded%20by%20saying%20that%20%E2%80%9CWe%20fail%20to%20understand%20as%20to%20how%20the%20human%20voice%20making%20azaan%20through%20loudspeaker%20in%20the%20morning%20could%20achieve%20the%20decibel%20%5Blevel%5D%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20creating%20noise%20pollution%20causing%20health%20hazards%20to%20the%20public%20at%20large%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20measurements%2Fassessment%20of%20noise%20pollution%20with%20the%20raising%20of%20decibel%20of%20sound%20is%20a%20scientific%20method%20wherein%20the%20sound%20created%20by%20a%20particular%20instrument%20etc%20can%20be%20measured%20to%20see%20that%20the%20sound%20caused%20by%20it%20is%20reaching%20beyond%20decibel%20permissible%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20such%20foundation%20has%20been%20laid%20in%20the%20petition%20to%20demonstrate%20that%20noise%20created%20by%20azaan%20for%20minutes%20at%20a%20stretch%20at%20different%20hours%20of%20the%20day%20would%20raise%20the%20level%20of%20the%20sound%20to%20cause%20noise%20pollution%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20then%20dismissed%20the%20PIL.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701268242000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F08102039%2F1200px-Gujarat-High-Court.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fgujarat-high-court-dismisses-pil-ban-azaan-loudspeakers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe%20fail%20to%20understand%20as%20to%20how%20the%20human%20voice%20making%20azaan%20through%20loudspeakers%20could%20achieve%20the%20decibels%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20creating%20noise%20pollution%20causing%20health%20hazard%20for%20%5Bthe%5D%20public%20at%20large%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chief%20Justice%20Agarwal%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fgujarat-high-court-dismisses-pil-ban-azaan-loudspeakers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Home%20Office%20doesn't%20know%20location%20of%2017%2C000%20asylum%20seekers%20-%20as%20Rwanda%20may%20get%20more%20than%20%C2%A3140m%20already%20paid%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701267900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F11%2F768x432%2Fskynews-rwanda-migrants-kigali_6362723.jpg%3F20231116151826%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Frwanda-may-be-getting-more-than-163140m-already-paid-as-home-offi