ruitments%2C%20likely%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftelangana%2Faspirants-in-limbo-as-tspsc-group-1-preliminary-gets-cancelled-yet-again%2Farticle67338527.ece%5C%22%3Eback-to-back%20exam%20cancellations%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Feducation%2Fnews%2Ftspsc-group-2-exam-2023-postponed-again-check-revised-schedule-at-tspsc-gov-in%2Farticleshow%2F104342366.cms%5C%22%3Erescheduling%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20party-wise%20highlights%20of%20what%20the%20electorate%20has%20been%20promised%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBRS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20manifesto%20%E2%80%93%20at%20least%20as%20it%20appears%20on%20its%20website%20%E2%80%93%20is%20compact%2C%20consisting%20of%20fifteen%20promises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20good%20chunk%20of%20these%20promises%20involves%20building%20on%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20existing%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20promised%20to%20gradually%20increase%20its%20flagship%20%E2%80%98Rythu%20Bandhu%E2%80%99%20scheme%2C%20currently%20amounting%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20per%20acre%20every%20year%20to%20land-owning%20farmers%2C%20to%20Rs%2016%2C000%20per%20acre%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20also%20says%20it%20will%20increase%20its%20existing%20monthly%20%E2%80%98pensions%E2%80%99%20gradually%20over%20its%20third%20term%20in%20power%20if%20elected.%20It%20proposes%20to%20increase%20its%20%E2%80%98Aasara%E2%80%99%20pension%2C%20given%20to%20a%20range%20of%20beneficiaries%20including%20widows%2C%20the%20elderly%2C%20AIDS%20patients%20and%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ebeedi%3C%2Fem%3E%20workers%2C%20from%20Rs%202%2C016%20per%20month%20to%20Rs%205%2C016%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20increase%20pensions%20to%20the%20physically%20handicapped%20from%20Rs%203%2C016%20per%20month%20to%20Rs%206%2C0