20are%20some%20of%20the%20other%20promises%20in%20the%20BRS%E2%80%99s%20manifesto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20detailed%20calendar%20promise%20is%20important%20as%20exam%20cancellations%20earlier%20this%20year%20put%20the%20BRS%20in%20a%20tight%20spot%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-polls-barrelakka-an-unemployed-youth-who-turned-cattle-herder-creates-ripples%5C%22%3Ecreating%20frustration%20among%20aspiring%20youth%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20providing%20ammunition%20to%20the%20growing%20opposition%20bloc%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20centrepiece%20of%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%2040-plus-page%20manifesto%20for%20Telangana%20is%20the%20%E2%80%98six%20guarantees%E2%80%99%20announced%20at%20its%20September%20public%20meeting%20near%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20its%20%E2%80%98Rythu%20Bharosa%E2%80%99%20guarantee%2C%20the%20Congress%20promises%20to%20give%20Rs%2015%2C000%20per%20acre%20to%20land-owning%20as%20well%20as%20tenant%20farmers%2C%20and%20Rs%2012%2C000%20every%20year%20to%20farm%20labourers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20similar%20to%20the%20BRS%E2%80%99%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20scheme%2C%20an%20important%20difference%20between%20the%20two%20is%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20promise%20to%20also%20pay%20tenant%20farmers%20and%20farm%20labourers%20%E2%80%93%20the%20BRS%E2%80%99s%20flagship%20scheme%20only%20benefits%20landholding%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20other%20guarantees%20are%20a%20monthly%20%E2%80%98pension%E2%80%99%20of%20Rs%204%2C000%20to%20a%20constituency%20consisting%20of%2C%20among%20others%2C%20senior%20citizens%2C%20widows%2C%20AIDS%20patients%20and%20beedi%20workers%20(very%20similar%20to%20the%20BRS%E2%80%99%20Aasara%20beneficiaries)%3B%20a%20monthly%20honorarium%20of%20Rs%202%2C500%20to%20women%3B%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20health%20insurance%20to%20eligible%20beneficiaries%20and%20gas%20cylinders%20at%20Rs%20500%20for%20those%20eligible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20offered%20benefits%2C%20including%20the%20amounts%20of%20financial%20assistance%2C%20are%20quite%20similar%20to%20those%20promised%20by%20the%20BRS%20%E2%80%93%20indeed%2C%20the%20BRS%20had%20attempted%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftelangana%2Fbrs-attempts-to-trump-congress-manifesto-with-few-more-novel-sops%2Farticle67424024.ece%5C%22%3Eone-up%20many%20of%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20guarantees%3C%2Fa%3E%20(some%20of%20which%20already%20resemble%20running%20BRS%20schemes)%20when%20it%20released%20its%20manifesto%20a%20month%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27132111%2FThe-Wire-91-1024x478.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27132111%2FThe-Wire-91-1024x478.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27132111%2FThe-Wire-91-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27132111%2FThe-Wire-91.png%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686533%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22392%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIts%20prospects%20for%20the%20polls%20initially%20written%20off%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20risen%20to%20become%20the%20primary%20opposition%20party%20in%20Telangana.%20Second%20from%20left%20is%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20state%20chief%20Revanth%20Reddy.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40INCIndia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remaining%20guarantees%20involve%20free%20electricity%20units%2C%20assistance%20in%20house-building%20for%20the%20homeless%20as%20well%20as%20for%20%E2%80%9Cfighters%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Telangana%20statehood%20movement%2C%20