rom%20the%20past%20relationship.%20Then%20we%20are%20expected%20to%20get%20data%20from%20the%20unorganised%20sector%20surveys%20at%20which%20point%20the%20estimates%20are%20corrected.%20The%20problem%20that%20has%20cropped%20up%20is%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%20several%20years%20since%20we%E2%80%99ve%20had%20an%20unorganised%20sector%20survey.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20they%E2%80%99re%20very%20unreliable%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYeah.%20So%20we%20are%20way%20out%20of%20whack%20from%20reality%20because%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20the%20reality%20is%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20which%20case%2C%20at%20the%20moment%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20clear%20or%20even%20a%20good%20idea%20of%20what%20is%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20unorganised%20sector.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETherefore%20the%207.8%25%20figure%20for%20quarter%201%20may%20be%20quite%20substantially%20inaccurate%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20based%20upon%20surveys%20that%20are%20several%20years%20old.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYeah%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20my%20personal%20reading%20on%20this%20is%20that%20yes%20it%20is%20overestimated.%20B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eecause%20what%20little%20one%20has%20seen%20from%20%E2%80%93%20sort%20of%2C%20what%20should%20I%20say%20%E2%80%93%20indirect%20data%2C%20the%20revival%20of%20the%20unorganised%20sector%20begins%20only%20sometime%20in%20late%202022.%20And%20perhaps%20even%20early%20this%20year.%20But%20the%20corporate%20sector%20has%20been%20doing%20extremely%20well.%20So%20the%20gap%20between%20corporate%20sector%20performance%20and%20the%20unorganised%20sector%20performance%2C%20I%20think%20grew%20very%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Esubstantially%20post-COVID.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhich%20means%20the%20proxy%20derived%20from%20the%20corporate%20sector%2C%20the%20organised%20sector%2C%20is%20increasingly%20wrong.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhich%20means%20then%20that%20not%20for%20the%20Ashoka%20Modi%20reason%2C%20not%20for%20the%20Subramanian%20and%20Felman%20reason%2C%20but%20for%20this%20third%20reason%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20one%20that%20you%E2%80%99ve%20discussed%20with%20me%20several%20times%20in%20the%20past%20%E2%80%93%20that%207.8%25%20figure%20for%20GDP%20growth%20in%20quarter%201%20is%20an%20overestimate%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20have%20any%20sense%20of%20how%20much%20it%E2%80%99s%20an%20overestimate%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20difficult%20to%20say.%20You%20know%2C%20the%20data%20that%20I%E2%80%99m%20relying%20on%20is%20essentially%20what%20has%20been%20happening%20to%20banking%20sector%20lending%20patterns.%20So%20bank%20lending%20to%20MSMEs%20had%20pretty%20much%20gone%20to%20zero%20until%20early%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethis%20year%20%E2%80%93%20February%20or%20March%20of%20this%20year.%20Then%20it%20starts%20picking%20up.%20And%20the%20informal%20sector%2C%20only%20part%20of%20the%20informal%20sector%20actually%2C%20is%20able%20to%20tap%20into%20that.%20So%20that%20was%20a%20very%20clear%20indication%20of%20the%20weakness%20among%20the%20unorganised%20sector%20units%20and%20the%20smaller%20units%20of%20the%20country%2C%20so%20the%20MSMEs.%20The%20point%20is%20we%20have%20no%20information%20on%20the%20alternatives%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Einformal%20sources%20of%20finance%20%E2%80%93moneylenders.%20Whether%20there%20was%20growth%20there%20or%20not%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20know.%20We%20only%20infer%20it%20when%20we%20look%20at%20data%20on%20unorganised%20sector%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eproduction%20and%20how%20much%20they%E2%80%99ve%20been%20getting%20from%20the%20formal%20sector%20and%20then%20you%20can%20