rably%20in%20the%20last%20decade.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYes%2C%20dramatically!%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20these%20are%20all%20reasons%20why%20when%20people%20doubt%20the%20accuracy%20of%20GDP%20calculation%20you%E2%80%99re%20giving%20them%20good%20reason%20to%20say%20your%20doubts%20are%20substantial.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYes%2C%20but%20it%20is%20not%20a%20problem%2C%20as%20I%20said%2C%20with%20the%20methodology.%20It%20is%20a%20problem%20with%20the%20data.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbsolutely%2C%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20glad%20you%20made%20that%20point.%20The%20methodology%20is%20good%2C%20given%20the%20circumstances%20is%20probably%20the%20best%20we%20could%20have.%20But%20the%20data%20that%20methodology%20uses%20is%20in%20some%20instances%20hugely%20out%20of%20date%20%E2%80%93%20by%2012%20years!%20Therefore%2C%20whatever%20the%20reason%2C%20the%20conclusion%20remains%20the%20same.%20Because%20the%20data%20is%20poor%2C%20the%20calculation%20of%20GDP%20is%20not%20that%20accurate%20and%20therefore%20the%20concerns%20you%20have%20about%20the%20accuracy%20are%20huge%20major%20concerns.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYes%2C%20they%20are%20concerns.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20I%20can%20say%20that%20these%20are%20huge%20major%20concerns%20that%20you%20have%20about%20the%20GDP%20outcome.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20right%20and%20what%20makes%20matters%20worse%20is%20that%20the%20concerns%20become%20even%20greater%20with%20the%20passage%20of%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20other%20words%20with%20every%20passing%20year%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3Eunless%20the%20data%20sources%20are%20updated%2C%20the%20concerns%20will%20grow.%20And%20there%20will%20in%20fact%20come%20a%20point%20when%20I%E2%80%99ll%20be%20forced%20to%20say%20this%20is%20unreliable.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20we%20getting%20close%20to%20that%20point%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20could.%20We%20are%20getting%20close%20to%2015%20years%20%5Bsince%20data%20sources%20have%20been%20updated%5D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20we%E2%80%99re%20getting%20very%20close%20to%20a%20point%20where%20you%20will%20say%20our%20GDP%20data%20is%20unreliable%20and%20the%20GDP%20outcome%20therefore%20is%20unreliable.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20figure%20that%20we%20boast%20about%20is%20unreliable.%20Okay%2C%20against%20that%20background%20%E2%80%93%20and%20I%20think%20that%E2%80%99s%20a%20very%20important%20background%20that%20we%20established%20for%20the%20audience%20%E2%80%93%20let%20me%20ask%20you%20the%20critical%20question%20that%20lies%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20this%20interview.%20How%20accurate%20or%20how%20misleading%20is%20GDP%20growth%20as%20a%20measure%20of%20the%20state%20of%20the%20economy%3F%20Before%20you%20answer%2C%20let%20me%20quote%20what%20Ashoka%20Modi%20wrote%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20October%2030%2C%20%E2%80%9CGDP%20is%20a%20flawed%20metric%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3Eof%20national%20economic%20welfare.%20It%20hides%20inequalities%20and%20deflects%20attention%20from%20acute%20job%20scarcity%2C%20poor%20education%2C%20and%20health%2C%20unlivable%20cities%2C%20a%20broken%20down%20judicial%20system%20and%20environmental%20damage.%E2%80%9D%20How%20close%20to%20correct%20is%20he%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20completely%20correct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECompletely%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20course.%20I%20may%20quibble%20with%20his%20phrasing%20but%20in%20substance%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20absolutely%20right.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%2C%20from%20a%20layman%E2%80%99s%20point%20of%20view%2C%20when%20GDP%20growth%20or