ore%20you%20get%20the%20truth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWell%2C%20it%20depends%20on%20what%20you%20mean%20by%20the%20truth.%20So%20you%20have%20the%20GDP%20and%20think%20of%20the%20GDP%20as%20the%20entire%20cake.%20Then%20you%20have%20to%20ask%20the%20question%3A%20how%20is%20that%20cake%20being%20distributed%20between%20the%20people%20in%20this%20country%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYes%2C%20but%20you%20could%20also%20ask%20another%20question.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20cake%20on%20the%20table%20looks%20enticing%20and%20the%20icing%20looks%20delectable%20but%20there%E2%80%99s%20an%20awful%20lot%20that%E2%80%99s%20not%20on%20the%20table%20that%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20see%20and%20how%20much%20is%20that%20losing%20out%20or%20missing%20out%20in%20telling%20the%20full%20story%3F%20Let%E2%80%99s%20come%20to%20that%2C%20because%20I%20think%20that%20is%20a%20major%20concern%20and%20let%E2%80%99s%20start%20with%20quarter%20one%20GDP%20cause%20it%20is%20the%20most%20recent%20figure%20we%20have%2C%207.8%25.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECorrect.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENow%2C%20it%20coincided%20with%20unemployment%20hovering%20around%208%25%20and%20apparently%20since%20then%20unemployment%20has%20shot%20up%20to%20over%2010%25%2C%20which%20Mahesh%20Vyas%20tells%20me%20is%20the%20highest%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%20for%2029%20months.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20right.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecondly%2C%20that%207.8%25%20figure%20also%20coincided%20with%20the%20highest%20demand%20for%20NREGA%20for%2010%20years%2C%20in%20the%20months%20of%20June%2C%20July%2C%20August.%20Now%2C%20when%20you%20look%20just%20at%20the%207.8%25%20figure%20on%20its%20own%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20reveal%20anything%20about%20high%20unemployment%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20reveal%20anything%20abo