s%20has%20been%20done%20through%20schemes%20such%20as%20distributing%20livestock%20to%20specific%20OBC%20groups%2C%20offering%20support%20to%20fishermen%2C%20and%20providing%20insurance%20for%20toddy%20tappers%20from%20the%20Goud%20caste.%20It%20established%20the%20Kula%20Vruthi%20OBC%20Development%20Fund%20(Kula%20Vruthi%20means%20caste%20occupation)%2C%20focusing%20on%20uplifting%20various%20OBC%20communities%20based%20on%20their%20traditional%20occupations.%20However%2C%20this%20approach%20has%20received%20severe%20criticism%20from%20several%20quarters%2C%20including%20OBCs%2C%20who%20say%20that%20such%20a%20policy%20has%20furthered%20the%20caste%20system%20by%20confining%20OBC%20groups%20to%20specific%20caste-based%20occupations%20rather%20than%20genuinely%20empowering%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F11140521%2F19399012_456485134706406_2038083548976842708_n.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F11140521%2F19399012_456485134706406_2038083548976842708_n.jpg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F11140521%2F19399012_456485134706406_2038083548976842708_n-300x230.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-319862%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22735%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EK.%20Chandrashekar%20Rao.%20Credit%3A%20Facebook%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20119%20seats%2C%20BRS%20has%20fielded%20only%2023%20OBCs%2C%20causing%20deep%20disappointment%20among%20these%20groups%20over%20underrepresentation.%20In%20particular%2C%20the%20influential%20Mudiraj%20community%20%E2%80%93%20according%20to%20various%20unofficial%20estimates%20constituting%20around%2012%25%