Madhu%20Yashki%20Goud%2C%20and%20Ponnam%20Prabhakar%2C%20had%20held%20a%20press%20conference%20at%20the%20party%20headquarters%20in%20Hyderabad%20requesting%20the%20party%20high%20command%20to%20increase%20representation%20for%20their%20communities%20in%20the%20nominee%20list.%20However%2C%20the%20party%20did%20not%20fulfil%20their%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27132111%2FThe-Wire-91.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27132111%2FThe-Wire-91.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27132111%2FThe-Wire-91-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27132111%2FThe-Wire-91-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686533%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECongress%20leaders%20Mallu%20Bhatti%20Vikramarka%2C%20Revanth%20Reddy%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20among%20others.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40INCIndia%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDejected%20with%20the%20candidate%20list%2C%20powerful%20OBC%20leader%20and%20former%20Telangana%20Congress%20chief%20Lakshmaiah%20left%20the%20party%20to%20join%20the%20BRS.%20Cheruku%20Sudhakar%2C%20another%20prominent%20OBC%20leader%2C%20followed%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20instance%2C%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20in%20order%20to%20woo%20the%20Mudiraj%20community%2C%20promised%20OBC%20leader%20Neelam%20Madhu%20a%20ticket%20from%20Patancheru%20after%20he%20was%20denied%20the%20same%20by%20the%20BRS.%20The%20party%20went%20back%20on%20its%20promise%20even%20after%20its%20national%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20had%20assured%20Madhu%20of%20the%20ticket.%20The%20Congress%20thus%20disappointed%20the%20Mudiraj%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20party%2C%20aware%20of%20the%20OBC%20vote%20bank%2C%20has%20been%20announcing%20several%20welfare%20measures%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20various%20sub-castes.%20During%20the%20electioneering%2C%20the%20party%20made%20a%20concerted%20effort%20to%20connect%20with%20OBC%20voters%20by%20raising%20their%20concerns%2C%20announcing%20a%20series%20of%20welfare%20measures%2C%20including%20conducting%20a%20caste%20census%2C%20allocating%20an%20OBC%20sub-quota%2C%20and%20ensuring%20reservations%20in%20proportion%20to%20the%20OBC%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20counter%20the%20BRS%20and%20BJP%20narrative%2C%20Congress%20has%20outlined%20a%20comprehensive%20plan%20for%20the%20welfare%20and%20development%20of%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBC).%20The%20party%20has%20promised%20to%20roll%20out%20a%20BC%20Sub%20Plan%2C%20by%20earmarking%20Rs%201%20lakh%20crore%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years%20for%20BC%20welfare.%20The%20party%20has%20also%20announced%20that%20it%20envisions%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20Most%20Backward%20Classes%20(MBC)%20Welfare%20department%20along%20with%20corporations%20for%20each%20BC%20caste.%20Reservations%20for%20BCs%20in%20local%20bodies%20and%20government%20contracts%20are%20to%20be%20increased%20to%2042%25%2C%20and%20special%20infrastructure%2C%20such%20as%20Professor%20Jayashankar%20BC%20Aikyatha%20Bhavans%2C%20will%20be%20established.%20OBC%20youth%20have%20been%20promised%20interest-free%20loans%20for%20business%20and%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20party%20pledges%20to%20move%20certain%20OBC%20communities%20to%20a%20more%20favourable%20reservation%20category%20and%20undertake%20initiatives%20like%20sheep%20distribution%20schemes%20for%20communities%20like%20Yadav%20and%20Kurma.%20The%20Mudiraj%20community%20and%20related%20castes%20%E2%80%98Mutrasi%20and%20Tenugollu%E2%80%99%20will%20be%20shifted%20from%20BC-D%20to%20BC-A%20in%20the%20reservation%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStrategic%20mistakes%20impact%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20OBC%20push%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20in%20other%20states%2C%20OBCs%20have%20emerged%20as%20the%20strong%20support%20base%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20Telangana%20in%20recent%20times.%20This%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20deliberate%20choice%20of%20handing%20over%20the%20reins%20of%20the%20party%20after%20the%20formation%20of%20Telangana%20in%202014%20to%20OBC%20leaders%3A%20K.%20Laxman%20and%20Bandi%20Sanjay.%20Its%20current%20top%20leadership%2C%20including%20Sanjay%20and%20Dharampuri%20Arvind%2C%20are%20from%20the%20Munnuru%20Kapu%20community%2C%20an%20influential%20OBC%20group%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20strategic%20accommodation%20of%20Eatala%20Rajendar%20of%20the%20Mudiraj%20community%20has%20also%20helped%20the%20BJP%20to%20woo%20OBC%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F06184339%2FUntitled-design-2022-07-06T184215.792.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F06184339%2FUntitled-design-2022-07-06T184215.792.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F06184339%2FUntitled-design-2022-07-06T184215.792-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F06184339%2FUntitled-design-2022-07-06T184215.792-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-606011%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFile%20photo.%20BJP%20Telangana%20unit%20former%20president