2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fthai-hostage-negotiator-thanks-iran-for-support-and-says-hamas-justified-in-taking-captives-13018272%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel-Hamas%20War%3A%20UN%20Experts%20Call%20for%20Investigation%20into%20'Crimes%20Against%20Humanity'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19092706%2FF8t8SUEWMAAvoa0.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EUnited%20Nations%20experts%2C%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20have%20appealed%20to%20all%20parties%20involved%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20to%20protect%20civilians%20and%20comply%20with%20their%20obligations%20under%20international%20law.%20They%20also%20called%20for%20independent%20investigations%20into%20allegations%20of%20war%20crimes%20and%20crimes%20against%20humanity%2C%20perpetrated%20in%20Israel%20and%20in%20the%20Occupied%20Palestinian%20Territory%20on%20October%207%20and%20thereafter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBelow%20is%20the%20full%20statement%20issued%20by%20the%20UN%20and%20the%20list%20of%20experts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGeneva%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20UN%20experts*%20today%20called%20for%20prompt%2C%20transparent%2C%20and%20independent%20investigations%20into%20allegations%20of%20war%20crimes%20and%20crimes%20against%20humanity%2C%20perpetrated%20in%20Israel%20and%20in%20the%20Occupied%20Palestinian%20Territory%20on%20October%207%2C%202023%20and%20thereafter.%20They%20urged%20all%20parties%20to%20the%20ongoing%20armed%20conflict%20to%20protect%20civilians%20and%20comply%20with%20their%20obligations%20under%20international%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndependent%20investigators%20must%20be%20given%20the%20necessary%20resources%2C%20support%20and%20access%20required%20to%20conduct%20prompt%2C%20thorough%20and%20impartial%20investigations%20into%20crimes%20allegedly%20committed%20by%20all%20parties%20to%20the%20conflict%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20experts%20said%2C%20calling%20on%20Israel%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20and%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ede%20facto%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0authorities%20in%20Gaza%20to%20cooperate%20fully%20with%20investigations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20duty%20to%20investigate%20war%20crimes%20and%20crimes%20against%20humanity%2C%20including%20any%20act%20of%20summary%20or%20extrajudicial%20killing%2C%20torture%20or%20other%20outrages%20on%20human%20dignity%2C%20is%20a%20fundamental%20legal%20obligation%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20experts%20urged%20the%20international%20community%20to%20ensure%20that%20all%20those%20responsible%20for%20war%20crimes%20and%20crimes%20against%20humanity%2C%20as%20well%20as%20any%20other%20international%20crimes%20committed%20in%20the%20conflict%2C%20especially%20persons%20with%20command%20responsibility%2C%20are%20promptly%20brought%20to%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20statute%20of%20limitation%20for%20such%20crimes%2C%20and%20they%20fall%20under%20universal%20jurisdiction%2C%20which%20means%20that%20courts%20in%20any%20country%20can%20exercise%20their%20authority%20to%20prosecute%20those%20responsible%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20nationality%20and%20the%20country%20where%20the%20crimes%20were%20committed%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20encourage%20all%20States%20to%20play%20a%20proactive%20role%20in%20identifying%20key%20suspected%20perpetrators%20and%20helping%20to%20facilitate%20prosecutions%20through%20the%20principle%20of%20mutual%20legal%20assistance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20experts%20recalled%20that%20reliable%20evidence%2C%20gathered%20by%20independent%20and%20impartial%20investigators%2C%20including%20forensic%20specialists%20experienced%20in%20investigating%20violations%20of%20international%20humanitarian%20law%2C%20is%20essential%20for%20successful%20prosecutions%2C%20and%20that%20investigations%20must%20comply%20with%20international%20standards.%20The%20experts%20referred%20to%20the%20Revised%20Manual%20on%20the%20Effective%20Investigation%20and%20Documentation%20of%20Crimes%20of%20Torture%20and%20Other%20Cruel%2C%20Inhuman%20or%20Degrading%20Treatment%20or%20Punishment%20(Istanbul%20Protocol)%20and%20the%20Revised%20United%20Nations%20Manual%20on%20the%20Effective%20Prevention%20and%20Investigation%20of%20Extra-Legal%2C%20Arbitrary%20and%20Summary%20Executions%20(Minnesota%20Protocol).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20welcomed%20ongoing%20investigations%20by%20the%20International%20Criminal%20Court%20and%20the%20Independent%20International%20Commission%20of%20Inquiry%20on%20the%20Occupied%20Palestinian%20Territory%2C%20including%20East%20Jerusalem%2C%20and%20Israel%2C%20to%20examine%20and%20document%20all%20existing%20evidence%20of%20crimes%20committed%20to%20date%20in%20Israel%2C%20Gaza%20and%20the%20West%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20stress%20that%20for%20the%20purposes%20of%20healing%2C%20recovery%2C%20reconciliation%20and%20justice%2C%20victims%20and%20survivors%2C%20and%20their%20families%2C%20should%20be%20able%20to%20participate%20in%20any%20proceedings%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20experts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20offered%20the%20support%20of%20their%20mandates%20and%20their%20expertise%2C%20including%20in%20forensic%20sciences%2C%20to%20advise%20and%20assist%20in%20this%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E*The%20experts%3A%20Morris%20Tidball-Binz%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2Fen%2Fspecial-procedures%2Fsr-executions%2Fabout-mandate%5C%22%3ESpecial%20Rapporteur%20on%20extrajudicial%2C%20summary%20or%20arbitrary%20executions%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20Alice%20Jill%20Edwards%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2Fen%2Fspecial-procedures%2Fsr-executions%2Fabout-mandate%5C%22%3ESpecial%20Rapporteur%20on%20Torture%20and%20Other%20Cruel%2C%20Inhuman%20or%20Degrading%20Treatment%20or%20Punishment%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESpecial%20Rapporteurs%20are%20part%20of%20what%20is%20known%20as%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2Fen%2Fspecial-procedures-human-rights-council%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%2Fen%2Fspecial-procedures-human-rights-council%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpecial%20Procedures%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20the%20Human%20Rights%20Council.%20Special%20Procedures%2C%20the%20largest%20body%20of%20independent%20experts%20in%20the%20UN%20Human%20Rights%20system%2C%20is%20the%20general%20name%20of%20the%20Council%E2%80%99s%20independent%20fact-finding%20and%20monitoring%20mechanisms%20that%20address%20either%20specific%20country%20situations%20or%20thematic%20issues%20in%20all%20parts%20of%20the%20world.%20Special%20Procedures%20experts%20work%20on%20a%20voluntary%20basis%3B%20they%20are%20not%20UN%20staff%20and%20do%20not%20receive%20a%20salary%20for%20their%20work.%20They%20are%20independent%20from%20any%20government%20or%20organization%20and%20serve%20in%20their%20individual%20capacity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701178251000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19092706%2FF8t8SUEWMAAvoa0.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-hamas-war-un-experts-call-for-investigation-into-crimes-against-humanity%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20statement%20issued%20by%20them%20urged%20all%20parties%20to%20the%20ongoing%20armed%20conflict%20to%20protect%20civilians%20and%20comply%20with%20their%20obligations%20under%20international%20law.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-hamas-war-un-experts-call-for-investigation-into-crimes-against-humanity%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Beware%20of%20smishing!%20What%20you%20need%20to%20know%20to%20stay%20safe%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701159476000%2C%22visual%22