C%20but%20at%20certain%20functions%20where%20I%20performed%20the%20song%20in%20front%20of%20government%20officials%2C%20they%20seemed%20to%20enjoy%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20song%20also%20makes%20clear%20references%20to%20the%20pride%20Moko%20feels%20in%20his%20Naga%20identity%20and%20the%20prejudices%20that%20people%20in%20mainland%20Indians%20harbour%20against%20Nagas%2C%20including%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F273338%2Fengineer-quits-job-pickle-business-nagaland-nitu-viluo-bengaluru%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efood%20habits%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBahar%20mannu%20ki%20ki%20kobi%20etu%20moi%20najane%20(Let%20people%20judge%20us%20because%20of%20our%20food%20habits%20and%20our%20ways)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMoi%20ki%20khai%20taikhan%20la%20ki%20jai%20(What%20I%20eat%20and%20how%20I%20look%20is%20none%20of%20their%20business)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMatha%20kati%20kena%20ahya%20manu%20asede%20(We%20came%20from%20a%20generation%20of%20headhunters)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMuikhan%20Naga%20manu%20khan%20bi%20kmoti%20nohoi%20de%20(We%20are%20all%20proud%20to%20be%20called%20a%20Naga)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCzbK1u_Kz5y%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCzbK1u_Kz5y%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3